name: Fitzwilliam Business Centre
tag_list: business-centre, office-space, meeting-rooms, virtual-office, business-address, office-space-ireland, virtual-office-ireland, virtual-office-dublin
overview:
Fitzwilliam Business Centre is Ireland’s leading provider of professional office space, virtual office solutions and meeting rooms with locations in Dublin, Drogheda, Navan, Naas and Prague. Fitzwilliam Business Centre’s serviced offices offer turn-key office space for small and medium enterprises supported by a state of the art IT infrastructure and innovative communications technology solutions.

Fitzwilliam Business Centre’s virtual office solutions are designed to appeal to small businesses who want to convey a professional image, but who do not want the overheads associated with renting office space and hiring dedicated staff. They are also ideal for companies wishing to setup a presence in Ireland without requiring physical office space. A range of virtual office plans are available including Bronze, Silver and Gold plans.

The Bronze Virtual Office plan is our entry level plan and offers incredible value for money. It is ideal for professionals working from home who do not require a dedicated telephone number and wish to avail of an exclusive business address to enhance their business image.

The Silver Virtual Office plan is our mid-level plan and offers a business address at an exclusive Fitzwilliam Business Centre location along with a dedicated telephone number with call forwarding to your preferred destination.

The Gold Virtual Office plan is a premium plan designed for businesses who want a turn-key business identity solution. With a business address, dedicated phone number and personalised call answering, you can always create the right impression.
